    <ul>
      <li><strong>Wi-Fi / BLE:</strong> ESP32, nRF52</li>
      <li><strong>sub-GHz:</strong> LoRa/FSK for long range</li>
      <li><strong>antennas:</strong> keep clearance; respect keep-outs; match ground plane advice</li>
    </ul>
    <Note variant="fact">follow module layout exactly; small antenna mistakes cost 20 dB.</Note>
  </article>
